metaInfo.metaTitle: Women's Clothing: Shop the Latest Trends & Fashion | Kohl's
metaInfo.copyBlock:
Shopping for Women's Clothing

Kohl's features an extensive selection of clothing for you to shop for. Looking for Apt. 9 or Croft & Barrow? We've got them, along with all your favorite fashion brands. When you're shopping for clothing, it's all about the right fit, and the right price. Kohl's makes it easy to find exactly what you need without regrets.

If you need a wardrobe overhaul, you'll find everything you need. Perhaps you just need the perfect companion item to take your outfit to new heights. You'll find it here at Kohl's. Offering the latest thing in fashion trends is one thing, but you can also find a great selection of petite and plus size clothing to choose from.

Picking your jumpsuits

Jumpsuits are hot. They're popular and they look good, so of course they are. But maybe you haven't seen how they've changed recently, which is why you need to check them out! The jumpsuits you will find here feature short and sleeveless styles, along with a myriad of colors and patterns. While there are plenty to sport on your days and nights off, there are so many that are great for work.

If you need something with less pant, consider snagging a romper. With their lighter and shorter design, you can accomplish several different looks with your accessories and color choices.

Picking your sweaters

Choosing a sweater is never hard. Choosing the right sweater can be. Kohl's makes it easy by breaking it all down for you:

When looking for a sweater consider the cut and occasion. If a pullover is what you need, you've got plenty of options from solid to patterned and if you need help cutting those frigid winds, you have hoodie options.

Don't forget cardigans either. They're the perfect outfit topper for nearly any season and occasion. Open fronts and ponchos are delightful for fall time work and play alike. The fashionable favorite is the long cardigan, which gives you a playful sway to your silhouette.

Picking your dresses

It's true, there's a lot of dresses. Shirt dresses. Formal dresses. Maxi, midi, and mini. Dresses for weddings. So many occasions and so many styles! So, where should you start?

Shirt dresses are great from leisure to business casual. Same goes for the maxi, midi, and mini dresses. These dresses feature increased versatility and comfort with their more flowing fits. While they're great choices year round, be sure to accessorize with the weather to maximize function and comfort.

Kohl's offers an excellent selection of dresses that are necessary buys for the next wedding you're attending. Prints, solid colors, stylish cuts… there's something for every taste and need. Weddings are fun places to experiment with different looks than you'd normally go for, so don't be afraid to get outside your comfort zone and enjoy the after party.

For formal events (black tie, prom, etc), you should find a dizzying selection of little black dresses, and evening wear for every size. For juniors, you'll surely find your dream dress for your prom. It's important to look your best, so don't be scared to steal the show!

Bottoms

There's far too many choices when it comes to bottoms, but that's okay! You can find shorts, skirts, pants, and just about anything you could possibly need. Casual bottoms pave the way for cute and playful outfits that can express who you really are. Business professional bottoms won't leave you worried about whether or not you look good enough. In fact, if styled right you might even look better than your best!

Activewear

Look, sometimes looking cute, extra, or otherwise can take a lot of work. Lazy mornings and Saturdays are more than okay, and that's why Kohl's offers an extensive selection of athletic clothing and sleepwear. You don't have to compromise being comfy and looking your best. Yeah, sometimes pajamas feel too cozy and relaxing, but that's why you can substitute them for athletic clothing. You can accomplish similar levels of comfort with the benefit of being able to hit the streets and be on the move.

When it comes to women's clothing at Kohl's, you can definitely up the ante on your fashion.
metaInfo.metaDescription: Enjoy free shipping and easy returns every day at Kohl's. Find great deals on Women's Clothing at Kohl's today!
